-- JPMorgan cuts jobs in leveraged finance
-- 
-- Thu Oct 11, 2007 3:00pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/11/us-jpmorgan-fixedincome-idUSWEN162420071011

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - JPMorgan Chase & Co ( JPM.N ) said on Thursday it was making modest staff reductions in areas that include structured credit and leveraged finance. 

 "We are making modest staff reductions in areas where we expect lower volumes going forward, including leveraged finance and structured credit," JPMorgan spokesman Brian J. Marchiony said.